txt.en: Destroy heraldry of Sauron in Parth Daenath ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
'The banners of the Dark Lord stand still upon the Corpse-fields!'
Heraldry of Sauron can be found in Parth Daenath.\n\nYou should destroy any heraldry of Sauron that you find in Parth Daenath.
'I no longer see the vile banners of Sauron!'
'What an insult! Can you believe this? The banners of the Dark Lord still stand upon the Corpse-fields! Rip them down before my dwarves see them!'
Heraldry of Sauron still waves in the winds throughout the Kingsland of Parth Daenath.
Durin IV can be found at Echad-in-Edhil.\n\nYou should talk to Durin IV.
'Well done! I no longer see the vile banners of Sauron, and the spirits of my dwarves will not be lowered by seeing the ugly things. Khazâd ai-mênu!'
